                Disability Resource Center
              











Test Scheduling Office Hours
Get hands-on support from our testing team to schedule your Fall 2022 accommodated exams!
Are you approved for testing accommodations but you're not sure how to schedule seats for testing in the DRC? DRC's Testing Team will be available to help you during our Testing Office Hours! No appointment necessary -- just swing by the DRC during any of the following drop-in times:
8/24/22 Wednesday 11AM - 1PM
8/25/22 Thursday 10AM - 12PM
8/26/22 Friday 1PM - 3PM
8/29/22 Monday 11AM - 1PM
8/30/22 Tuesday 10AM - 12PM
9/02/22 Friday 12PM - 2PM
Please bring your syllabus and laptop or tablet
1200 W. Harrison St., Room 1070 SSB (MC 321), Chicago, IL 60607
 
Want to try scheduling on your own first? Check out our online test scheduling instructions.














 
